title: Dutch Treat Update I131-155 (Indie Playlists July-September 2013
description:
25 New 2-hour playlists (over 750 of the best quality tracks = 10%) for the Dutch Treat Indie Collection. These lists may contain some minor corrections and has been renumbered for accessibility reasons and the use in a car. You dont know and you do not want it all? For Songs of the heart choose: _I148 2 Love Is Hard, for Lounge; _I137 1 Breeze. for Romantic Pop; _I140 2 Building Bridges. For Electro Rock; _I152 3 Space. For Solid Rock; _I131 4 Your Wish or _I133 4 Rootless. And for Symphonic Rock Lovers, my personal favorite: _I135 3 Deprived... Or pick any other, depending on the type of list you like..... Enjoy,

Types of Playlists (Number directly behind the serial number):

 1 = Soft Pop and Folk, top sound quality
 2 = A mix of Rock and Pop, a bit more extreme and little less sound quality
 3 = Electronic, varying from chill to Rock
 4 = Solid Rock
 5 = Garage Rock and Dance

Oh Yes, I almost forgot to thank all other idiots making their Indie heard by making Playlists. Please take care in passing it through. Quality, cuts, labels, volume and stuff. I think the Artists would appreciate it (and the listeners too).
